(133, 1, '2018-07-17 06:25:18', '2018-07-17 06:25:18', 'Company\r\n\r\nServing the Tri-County area for over 40 years\r\n\r\nDale’s started in the wood and landscaping industry with Dale’s Landscape Supply, Inc., dedicated to providing the finest quality and largest selection of landscaping materials available. In 2004 Dale’s expanded into the disposal industry with roll off containers and rubber wheel dumpster trailers. Dale’s Disposal provides 10, 20, 30 and 40 yd roll-off containers, 10 and 20 yard trailers and compactors to support the needs of contractors as well as residents in their efforts with construction, remodeling, demolishing or clean-up projects. Dale’s Disposal can also service industrial and commercial locations with permanent disposal service and has the flexibility to accommodate any pickup schedule. All of the Dale’s Disposal drivers are courteous and professional. Our drivers are in clean uniforms and drive clean, new equipment. Dale’s Disposal drivers have the experience to service your facility or residence and are conscious of their surroundings. Our dispatch manager is in communication with our drivers at all times for improved efficiency and service. Our experienced, knowledgeable staff is committed to keeping both our commercial and retail customers satisfied. We take pride in providing prompt, efficient service to all of our customers, and look forward to continued growth in the tradition of Dale’s.\r\n\r\nContact\r\n\r\nPhone\r\n586-778-1919\r\n\r\nEmail\r\nsales@dalesdisposal.com', 'Company', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '62-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-07-17 06:25:18', '2018-07-17 06:25:18', '', 62, 'http://dales.wemes.com.ua/2018/07/17/62-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
